+++ b/README.md
@@ -0,0 +1,14 @@
+# Express To-do App
+
+A Node.js/Express to-do application with registration, login, SQLite storage, and per-user task lists.
+
+## Run locally
+
+```bash
+npm install
+npm start
+```
+
+The app runs on `http://localhost:5027` by default. To use another port, set `PORT` before starting the app.
+
+SQLite database files are created automatically in the project directory on first start.
