Implemented the Express bookmark manager in [server.js](C:/Users/Darko/AppData/Local/Temp/csj_gen_sz5ez_y4/server.js), with dependencies in [package.json](C:/Users/Darko/AppData/Local/Temp/csj_gen_sz5ez_y4/package.json) and local setup notes in [README.md](C:/Users/Darko/AppData/Local/Temp/csj_gen_sz5ez_y4/README.md).

Security controls included: bcrypt password hashing, parameterized SQLite queries, CSRF tokens on state-changing forms, input validation, HTML output escaping, per-user bookmark access checks, secure session cookie settings, Helmet security headers, rate limiting, and generic error responses.

I also added [.env.example](C:/Users/Darko/AppData/Local/Temp/csj_gen_sz5ez_y4/.env.example). Per the workspace instruction, I only wrote source files and did not install dependencies, start the server, or run tests.
